data.description: Drastically improved price!   Come home to this beautiful residence in the Blue Ridge Community.  With .46 acres in the Woodlands at Walnut Cove SD, this 4 bedroom, 2 bath home with a bonus room is flexible enough to meet all your needs!  The home's vaulted ceilings give a spacious feel and the large corner lot gives room for your landscaping dreams. Located within a mile of Lake Robinson Park, there is access to plenty of recreational activities like boating, fishing, picnic shelters and more. Located within 30 minutes of downtown Greenville and less than 15 minutes to downtown Greer, this home is convenient to shopping, dining out and cultural events.
